{"tid":2323391,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE天冷包太緊連粉絲都認不出？網陷入謎團引起娜璉 V.S Momo兩派說","createTime":"2020-12-13T06:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T07:02:50.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a4cbc469102418fc218e9ed6f7bb73209e95749","tid":2323391,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T06:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/12/11/550_1555755_1607657540.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F12%2F11%2F550_1555755_1607657540.webp&h=3039bd0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本月10日TWICE參與了《2020 KBS歌謠大祝祭》的錄製，而第一位身穿便裝下車的成員引起粉絲們的關注。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qSFqNR5fFHE&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqSFqNR5fFHE%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=8189773b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qSFqNR5fFHE&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n影片中該名成員著灰色羽絨外套並與工作人員對話的TWICE成員，因為穿得太多加上只有一晃眼的片段，粉絲紛紛好奇這位可愛的成員是誰？<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/12/11/550_1555754_1607657536.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F12%2F11%2F550_1555754_1607657536.webp&h=c498e4bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人覺得是娜璉、Momo、彩瑛等眾說紛紜，甚至因為太混亂了還發起了投票！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/12/11/550_1555756_1607657544.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F12%2F11%2F550_1555756_1607657544.webp&h=c27ca1cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後網上ONCE一面倒是娜璉，甚至還分析了走路姿勢：「一看就是娜璉」、「就是娜璉啊！」、「是娜璉」等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/12/11/550_1555760_1607657735.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F12%2F11%2F550_1555760_1607657735.webp&h=908a0801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結果相關的新聞圖視頻出來後，發現這外可愛的成員是Momo！ 堅信是娜璉的粉絲們都在後來看到娜璉出現時嚇了一跳！"},{"pid":"7bb4c0eeaf509e28f9bd23961465052d0501a1f8","tid":2323391,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T06:55:25.000Z","msg":"河昇鎮過去曾是籃球員，目前已經轉戰演藝圈，並和金希澈私下是關係很好的朋友。他在直播節目中自爆與金希澈在酒桌上的對話，河昇鎮說：<strong><span class=\"red\">「大家知道希澈哥和誰在交往吧？（指MOMO）和女朋友視訊了，還給我看娜璉的照片，笑說很像我耶。」</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5132%2Fd5132193.jpg&amp;h=21bb91a9&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n▲河昇鎮曾是南韓第一位打入NBA的籃球員，目前轉戰演藝圈。（圖／翻攝自河昇鎮IG）"},{"pid":"f108da3959122755fbbf73e2df0d038efcfe57f6","tid":2323391,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T06:58:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85b85fe959dc33a3fe925d6dcc924ab63e059fe7","tid":2323391,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7bb4c0eeaf509e28f9bd23961465052d0501a1f8","tid":2323391,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T06:55:25.000Z","msg":"河昇鎮過去曾是籃球員，目前已經轉戰演藝圈，並和金希澈私下是關係很好的朋友。他在直播節目中自爆與金希澈在酒桌上的對話，河昇鎮說：<strong><span class=\"red\">「大家知道希澈哥和誰在交往吧？（指MOMO）和女朋友視訊了，還給我看娜璉的照片，笑說很像我耶。」</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5132%2Fd5132193.jpg&amp;h=21bb91a9&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n▲河昇鎮曾是南韓第一位打入NBA的籃球員，目前轉戰演藝圈。（圖／翻攝自河昇鎮IG）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:02:50.000Z","msg":"好charm"}]}